            <div>
                <head>Comments</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:07:32.562+09:00">Stunning example: could be one of the earliest in the Chinese language - if it really means what you say it does, that is.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:11:15.792+09:00">But how can I not speak up on this? is what I think this must mean, no?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:12:04.026+09:00">don't try to avoid ritual prohibitions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:15:18.993+09:00">and bring everyone...</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:16:53.713+09:00">your bringing up this problem</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:17:50.137+09:00">Now the bandit's assault on people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:18:47.687+09:00">is simply without basis in justice</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.69" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:22:14.156+09:00">In principle</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.76" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:26:49.07+09:00">Ah: the threat!!!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.80" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:28:47.857+09:00">Don't behave like the hoi polloi who, whenever they feel like saying something go on talking.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.173" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T23:33:32.111+09:00">and let him consider for himself CH</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.146" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T23:41:37.152+09:00">So those who will be taken to court on this and will risk losing their lives</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.147" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T23:42:39.976+09:00">will be more than one person.</seg>
                </p>
